{
  "texts": [
    "The task requires the model to choose the most suitable option that correctly resolves the reference in response to the question.",
    "We use 1100 data points from the newly annotated MetoQA dataset for this task.",
    "We have selected two evaluation methods namely length normalized Cloze prompting (Brown et al., 2020) and Multiple Choice Prompting (MCP) (Robinson and Wingate, 2023) considering the capabilities of all the models.",
    "We have also computed the Proportion of Plurality Agreement (PPA) (Robinson and Wingate, 2023) for all the models to ensure the model's consistency across possible orders of answer options.",
    "The results for PPA are presented in Figure 3."
  ]
}